## 📱 Supreme Responsive Grid System - Grid-Mod.js

### ⭐ Innovation Highlight: Agentic Grid Intelligence
The `grid-mod.js` represents the pinnacle of modern grid architecture - an intelligent, self-optimizing responsive system featuring:

- **Performance optimization**: Throttled events, caching, lazy loading
- **Visual debugging**: Console logging and development indicators
- **Smart animations**: Smooth transitions and visual feedback
- **CSS variable integration**: Dynamic theming support

### 1. Grid-Mod Usage

#### Advanced Features
```html
<!-- Auto-named grid with animations -->
<div screen="6,3,2,1" gap="var(--gap-md)">
  <!-- Becomes automatically -->
</div>
```

### 2. Breakpoint System
- **Small**: ≤480px (mobile)
- **Semi**: ≤768px (tablet)  
- **Medium**: ≤1024px (desktop)
- **Large**: >1024px (large screens)

### 3. Semantic Grid Patterns
Apply grid attributes to parent containers with meaningful class names:

```html
<!-- Feature showcase grid -->
<section class="feature-grid" screen="4,3,2,1" gap="var(--gap-md)">
  <div>Innovation 1</div>
  <div>Innovation 2</div>
  <div>Innovation 3</div>
</section>

<!-- Product display grid -->
<div class="product-grid" screen="3,2,2,1" gap="var(--gap-lg)">
  <!-- Products auto-arrange -->
</div>

<!-- Team showcase grid -->
<div class="team-grid" screen="4,2,1,1" gap="var(--gap-md)">
  <!-- Team members layout -->
</div>
```

**Common Patterns:**
- **Feature Grid**: 4,3,2,1 - Standard feature sections
- **Product Grid**: 3,2,2,1 - E-commerce layouts
- **Team Grid**: 4,2,1,1 - Team member cards
- **Gallery Grid**: 4,3,2,1 - Photo galleries
- **Card Grid**: 3,2,2,1 - Content cards

### 4. Advanced Configuration Options
```javascript
